{"id":295628,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-美辰集资案受害人到陕西省政府上访（图/","date":"2013-05-28T05:45:38Z","modified":"2013-05-28T05:45:38Z","title":"维权网 | 美辰集资案受害人到陕西省政府上访（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员于富民报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日上午</span><span>，美辰集资案受害人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>多受害者到陕西省政府上访，坚决要求依法作出判决，查处合谋诈骗的官员和徇私枉法的办案人员，追回他们的钱财。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>以下是这些美辰集资案受害人的上访说明：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>西安美辰科技股份有限公司与政府官员勾结，诈骗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>亿多元，案件调查审理七年了，至今没有判决，被诈骗的钱一分都没有给我们退还。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>美辰科技股份有限公司法人是陈美英。陈梅英从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2001</span><span>年开始就以开发生物高科技产品的名义在社会上广泛招股。她出示了陕西省发改委对于她高科技生物制品报告的审查批复和对于美辰公司增资扩股的批示，宣传她的公司将在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年前在美国上市，如到期不能在美国上市，则给入股人退款，并给每年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10%</span><span>的利息，等等。到了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年，不见美辰公司在美国上市，入股的资金也不给退还，更谈不上利息。美辰公司先是拖延，后是欺骗，再后来连人都很难找到。我们受骗的入股人于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月报案，案件由西安市公安局高新分局调查处理，陈梅英于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年才被逮捕。此案在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年移交西安市中级人民法院审理，西安中院已经</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>次将案子发回公安机关，要求补充侦查，至今没有判决。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据我们了解到的情况，陈梅英的美辰公司是一个空壳公司，陈与政府官员勾结集资诈骗，范围达到全国十几个城市，被骗的入股人有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>千多人，仅在陕西就有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1400</span><span>多人，诈骗的总金额有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>亿多元。陕西省发改委副主任李晓东在此案中有赖不掉的责任。我们入股者大多数是花甲以上的离退休人员，拿出的是我们的养老钱、活命钱。仅我们调查到的情况，有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">46</span><span>位入股者在数年漫长的追讨中因焦虑悲愤而死亡。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">                   </span><span>美辰集资案全体受害的入股人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">                       2013<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">年</span></span>5<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span></span>23<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日</span></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></span></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-GkUrzn2ZG2g/UaQYceSdauI/AAAAAAAAinI/-0YYINFlKLY/s1600/DSCN3680.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-GkUrzn2ZG2g/UaQYceSdauI/AAAAAAAAinI/-0YYINFlKLY/s320/DSCN3680.JPG\" width=\"288\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-GkUrzn2ZG2g/UaQYceSdauI/AAAAAAAAinI/-0YYINFlKLY/s1600/DSCN3680.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-GkUrzn2ZG2g/UaQYceSdauI/AAAAAAAAinI/-0YYINFlKLY/s1600/DSCN3680.JPG\" /></a></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4ELteDcSFPs/UaQa-ss3gcI/AAAAAAAAino/q1QduQsBJ4o/s1600/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130528094854.png\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"237\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4ELteDcSFPs/UaQa-ss3gcI/AAAAAAAAino/q1QduQsBJ4o/s320/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130528094854.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qBy0C5neHOY/UaQbAYRlZ0I/AAAAAAAAinw/guiHoipxTg8/s1600/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130528094835.png\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"232\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qBy0C5neHOY/UaQbAYRlZ0I/AAAAAAAAinw/guiHoipxTg8/s320/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130528094835.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hxKIMZehqTo/UaQYdS4x_2I/AAAAAAAAinQ/qWfNfxSGcuU/s1600/DSCN3677.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hxKIMZehqTo/UaQYdS4x_2I/AAAAAAAAinQ/qWfNfxSGcuU/s1600/DSCN3677.JPG\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-AwPMO0ZPXZs/UaQYnsIwW9I/AAAAAAAAinY/1DcpeiSZHq4/s1600/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130528094854.png\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-AwPMO0ZPXZs/UaQYnsIwW9I/AAAAAAAAinY/1DcpeiSZHq4/s1600/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130528094854.png\" /></a></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-AwPMO0ZPXZs/UaQYnsIwW9I/AAAAAAAAinY/1DcpeiSZHq4/s1600/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130528094854.png\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-AwPMO0ZPXZs/UaQYnsIwW9I/AAAAAAAAinY/1DcpeiSZHq4/s1600/QQ%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE20130528094854.png\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></span></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}